review_blob: A bomber from my facorite brother in maw that lives in Chicago, great flavored Ipa, pretty much my wheelhouse for what i like.
Decent, not as good as others from this brewery. I drank it with my mouth.................  ...
Great body, appearance, and aroma. A bit too malty for my pallate, which has been the case in most imperials I have experienced.
Wow. Great. Strong. A+, pleasant surprise from an otherwise clueless waitress. I would drink again.
Very drinkable, awesome aroma. From the local micro/macro brewery, so probably pretty fresh. I would drink this again!
